body_html:
@Hunterwolf88 The options I can think of to address these warnings:

  1. Make sure your version is the latest master 1.7.0.
  2. Following the Bazel install guide: https://docs.bazel.build/versions/master/install-ubuntu.html
  3. Make Bazel point at com_google_protobuf by default for cc/java_proto_library rules.
    Please make sure these three options.

@Hunterwolf88  The options I can think of to address these warnings:
  1. Make sure your version is the latest master 1.7.0.
  2. Following the Bazel install guide: https://docs.bazel.build/versions/master/install-ubuntu.html
  3. Make Bazel point at com_google_protobuf by default for cc/java_proto_library rules.
Please make sure these three options.
